  <title>Motion Point</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Motion-Point</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Motion-Point</text>: a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> that is constrained to move along a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-path</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">We add a </text><text styleclass="Interface">Motion-Point</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> to the sketch-path with the command: </text><text styleclass="T_Menusmall">Add Motion-Path FB. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">You can edit the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Path FB</text> to increase the number of <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Motion-Points</text> on the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">sketch-path</text>, and move their starting position on the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-path</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Motion-Path">Add Motion-Path FB</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Loop">Sketch-Path</link>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
